doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Terms and Conditions | MCYAM Food Exchange
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="/css/auth-terms.css")

  body.terms-page-body
    .terms-page
      header.terms-header
        a.terms-logo-link(href="/login")
          img.terms-logo(src="/images/logo.png", alt="MCYAM Food Exchange logo")

        nav.terms-nav
          a(href="/login") Login
          a(href="/register") Create account

      main.terms-main
        section.terms-hero
          span.terms-badge MCYAM Food Exchange
          h1 Terms and Conditions
          p These Terms and Conditions explain the basic rules for using MCYAM Food Exchange. By creating an account, you agree to use the platform responsibly, provide accurate food listing information, respect other users, and follow food safety expectations.

        section.terms-card
          ol.terms-list
            li
              h2 Respectful Use of the Platform
              p Users must treat all other users with respect. Rude, abusive, threatening, discriminatory, or inappropriate behaviour will not be tolerated on the platform.

            li
              h2 Account Responsibility
              p Users are responsible for the information they provide when creating an account. Users must not create fake accounts, impersonate another person, or misuse another user’s account.

            li
              h2 Accurate Food Listings
              p Users must provide honest and accurate information when creating a food listing. This includes the food name, description, quantity, collection location, pickup time, expiry date, allergens, and any relevant storage information.

            li
              h2 Food Safety
              p Users must only list food that is safe to share. Food that is contaminated, spoiled, incorrectly stored, or unsafe for consumption must not be listed on the platform.

            li
              h2 Expiry Dates and Allergen Information
              p Users must not change, hide, or misrepresent expiry dates or allergen information. Any known allergen or dietary information should be clearly stated in the listing description.

            li
              h2 Collection and Pickup Responsibility
              p MCYAM is a food exchange platform only. Users are responsible for arranging and completing the agreed collection or handover of food. The platform is not responsible for delivering food items.

            li
              h2 Claiming Food
              p When a user requests to claim food, the listing owner may accept or decline the request. A claim is only confirmed once the listing owner accepts it.

            li
              h2 Communication and Behaviour
              p Users must communicate politely and honestly when arranging collection. Any misuse, harassment, or repeated failure to collect agreed food may result in account restrictions.

            li
              h2 Reporting Issues
              p Users can report listings that appear unsafe, misleading, expired, or inappropriate. Reported listings may be reviewed and removed if they break the platform rules.

            li
              h2 Platform Responsibility
              p MCYAM helps connect users who want to share or claim surplus food. The platform does not guarantee the quality, condition, or safety of food listed by users. Users should use their own judgement before sharing or collecting food.

            li
              h2 Privacy
              p Users should not share unnecessary personal information publicly. Pickup details should only be shared where needed for collection purposes.

            li
              h2 Agreement to Terms
              p By creating an account, users confirm that they have read, understood, and agreed to follow these Terms and Conditions.

          .terms-actions
            a.terms-primary-button(href="/register") Back to create account
            a.terms-secondary-button(href="/login") Login instead

      footer.terms-footer
        p © 2026 MCYAM Food Exchange. All rights reserved.
